import React from 'react'
  import { MDXTag } from '@mdx-js/tag'
  

export default ({components, ...props}) => <MDXTag name="wrapper"  components={components}><MDXTag name="h1" components={components} props={{"id":"tundra-ui"}}>{`Tundra UI`}</MDXTag>
<MDXTag name="ul" components={components}>
<MDXTag name="li" components={components} parentName="ul"><MDXTag name="strong" components={components} parentName="li">{`It’s consistent`}</MDXTag>{`. `}</MDXTag>
<MDXTag name="li" components={components} parentName="ul"><MDXTag name="strong" components={components} parentName="li">{`It’s self-contained`}</MDXTag>{`. `}</MDXTag>
<MDXTag name="li" components={components} parentName="ul"><MDXTag name="strong" components={components} parentName="li">{`It’s reusable`}</MDXTag>{`.`}</MDXTag>
<MDXTag name="li" components={components} parentName="ul"><MDXTag name="strong" components={components} parentName="li">{`It’s robust`}</MDXTag></MDXTag>
</MDXTag></MDXTag>
